text: Vihanti is a former municipality in Northern Ostrobothnia, Finland. Since 2013, it became a part of the city of Raahe. As of 31 December 2012, 3,020 people lived there. Neighbouring municipalities are Haapavesi, Oulainen, Pyhäjoki, Raahe, Siikajoki and Siikalatva. == Other websites == * Municipality of Vihanti – Official website Category:Former municipalities of Finland
title: Vihanti
